                "name": "width",
                "value": "",
                "type": "query"
              },
              {
                "name": "height",
                "value": "",
                "type": "query"
              },
              {
                "name": "format",
                "value": "",
                "type": "query"
              }
            ]
          },
          "docs": "OGC Web Map Service entry point. Use `request=GetCapabilities` to list layers or `request=GetMap` to render an image of an area of interest."
